num=float(input("Enter the rupee:"))
#1rupee=100 paise 
split_num=str(num).split(".")
c=split_num[0]
#comverting rupee to paise and printing
paise=(int(c)*100)+int(split_num[1])
print(f"Rupee {num} in paise {paise}")
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Output 1
Enter the rupee:9.98
Rupee 9.98 in paise 998
Output 2
Enter the rupee:0.05
Rupee 0.05 in paise 5


